(1842, 1, '2015-07-22 01:16:18', '2015-07-22 01:16:18', '<div class="contentdiv">\r\n<h2>Partnerships and Consulting Solutions</h2>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000080;"><a title="Indaba1" href="http://www.indaba1.com/default.aspx" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000080;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>Indaba</strong></span></span></a> </span>- <span style="font-size: small;">Providing Excellence in Leadership and Management, through the provision of E-learning tools and solutions for companies of all sizes</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-size: small;"><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Indaba        Global''s World Leading Online Leadership Programs:</span> </strong>Using Patent Pending        technology, Indaba Global has created extensive MBA-like online coaching        and training materials on a wide range of<span style="color: #006699;"><strong> <a title="Programs" href="http://www.indaba1.com/online-programs.aspx" target="_blank">programs</a></strong></span> so that employees        and leadership have the knowledge required to enable them to work through        a myriad of challenges. In addition, Indaba Global has developed a<span style="color: #006699;"> </span><a title="Software" href="http://www.indaba1.com/software_platform.aspx" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #006699;"><strong>software        platform</strong></span></span></a><span style="color: #0099cc;"> </span>that is customizable and may be private-labeled with complete flexibility        offering secure access to online video training, audio, and testing. <strong>NEW:</strong> DISC Assessment + Customized eLearning</span> = <a title="DISCflex" href="http://www.discflex.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #006699;"><strong><span style="font-size: small;">DISCflex</span></strong></span><span style="color: #006699; font-size: small;">™</span></a><span style="color: #006699;">.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;"><span style="color: #006699;"><strong><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000080;"><a title="Prevue" href="http://www.prevuehr.com" target="_blank">Prevue</a></span> -</span></strong> </span></span><span style="font-size: small;">Tools for determining the profile of ideal candidates</span></p>\r\n<div class="post-content">\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>The Prevue Assessment System</strong>, provides businesses and human resource professionals with a suite of reports that assist in human resource decision-making.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">The Prevue Questionnaire is based on the ICES Plus Assessment Test,  an accurate, valid and reliable psychometric assessment that measures  work-related characteristics of people through their responses to a set  of questions.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">The Prevue Assessment is a pre-employment  and or post-employment  tool that can be used for structured employment interviewing and or  coaching</span></p>\r\n<p><a title="Assess to Succeed" href="http://www.assesstosucceed.com" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000080;"><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Assess to Succeed</span></strong></span></a></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">Assess to Succeed specialises in helping you to make better decisions with your staff  selection and development, along with assisting individuals with  lifelong learning. An assessment can be used as part of the selection  process for job interviews, job matching as a coaching tool and or for  succession planning.  There are a number of Psychometric Assessments and  training programmes that do not have the ability to be used at any  level in organisations.  At Assess to Succeed.....<a title="ASSESS T S more" href="http://www.assesstosucceed.com">more</a></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Consulting Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1764-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-22 01:16:18', '2015-07-22 01:16:18', '', 1764, 'http://localhost/mysite/wordpress/2015/07/22/1764-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
